These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, designer
1. the engineer is on the left or right of the designer##3
2. the designer is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | engineer | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | dancing | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | trance |

